extendedInfo.description: *This Game Requires Flash Player.Description:Every day, runners are sent from the glade to map out the interminable maze that's holding them captive.Do you have what it takes to become a maze runner?Controls:use <, >, ^, v to move Original Creator:The Maze Runner--------------This game has been ported to android from http://www.flashgamedistribution.com. Original Branding and advertising has been kept in tact and no alterations have been made from the original shockwave file in any way.
